  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_76CA51B0-2221-0135-7189-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If Profiles is not enabled for your institution, you can view the Membership Section by clicking the <strong>more user details </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="limit_user_to_section" data-step-uuid="3874A194-55DF-4D33-A829-F4E2B6D040C1">
    <h2 id="limit_user_to_section" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Limit User to Section</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/782/725/original/90dc8f36-1343-4e15-99fc-2c3bb05a484d.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/782/725/medium/90dc8f36-1343-4e15-99fc-2c3bb05a484d.png" srcset="" alt="Limit User to Section" height="307" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_76CA8490-2221-0135-718B-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Limit this user to only see fellow section users</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="let_user_see_all_sections" data-step-uuid="A64795D8-C8F2-4CDC-9325-0C0D815B150B">
    <h2 id="let_user_see_all_sections" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Let User See All Sections</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/782/727/original/99948780-1f83-4dba-9c94-92276d17a3fc.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/782/727/medium/99948780-1f83-4dba-9c94-92276d17a3fc.png" srcset="" alt="Let User See All Sections" height="306" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_76CAC6C0-2221-0135-718D-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Verify the user can only view students in their section.</p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: If you want to allow the student to view students in any course section again, click the <strong>let this user see all course users</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
